Quickstrike/Cheetor:



"Let's search that Maxie out and take 'im out!" Quickstrike announced. He 
stepped to the side, studing the area where he hear the snap. He held out 
his cobra arm, with the mouth of it gaped. He walked until he saw a patch of 
dull yellow and small black blots.


"Uh-oh," Cheetor whispered as he saw the Fuzor come tredding towards him. He 
pinned his ears, and crouched lower. Two against one--no three against one. 
Scorponok was there. But how did that happen?
